lead_paragraph: French Open champion Stan Wawrinka and Milos Raonic meet for the fifth time when they play a fourth-round match Monday at the Australian Open. The 25-year-old Canadian hopes their first meeting in a Grand Slam tournament will go better than the previous four in non-majors.

headline.print_headline: What to Watch on Monday, Day 8 at the Australian Open
